#: ../../controlpanel.rst:404
msgid "A \"Hardware Compatibility\" icon in Control Panel provides a quick overview of the system's detected hardware. To start the application, double-click its icon in Control Panel or type :command:`pc-sysinstaller -checkhardware`."
