#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1141
msgid "Click the \"Keyboard model\" drop-down menu to select the type of keyboard. Note that the default model of \"Generic 104-key PC\" does **not** support special keys such as multimedia or Windows keys. You will need to change this default to enable support for hot keys."
