#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1144
msgid "To add another keyboard layout, click the \"+\" button, which will open the screen shown in :numref:`Figure %s: Adding Another Layout <keyboard2>`. Highlight the desired layout. This will activate the \"Layout variant\" drop-down menu where you can select to either use the \"Typical\" variant or a specific variant. Press \"OK\" to add the configured layout."
