"establecer las teclas de accerso rápido de la distribución del teclado."

#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1166
msgid "If you wish to set the keys for terminating the graphical session, check the box \"Ctrl+Alt+Backspace terminates xorg\"."
msgstr ""
"Si desea establecer las teclas para terminar la sesión gráfica, seleccione "
"la casilla \"Ctrl+Alt+Retroceso termina xorg\"."

#: ../../controlpanel.rst:1168
msgid "To configure many more keyboard shortcuts, click the \"Advanced view\" button which will open the screen shown in :numref:`Figure %s: Configuring Keyboard Shortcuts <keyboard4>`. In this example, several categories have been expanded to show their options. To enable an option, check its box."
